patthana8.29:1.1_0: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo
patthana8.29:1.1_1: uppajjati hetupaccayā. Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naaganthaniyo
patthana8.29:1.1_2: ceva nano ca gantho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca
patthana8.29:1.1_3: dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho
patthana8.29:2.1_0: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naaganthaniyo ceva nanogantho
patthana8.29:2.1_1: ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca
patthana8.29:2.1_2: nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Naaganthaniyañceva nano
patthana8.29:2.1_3: ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano
patthana8.29:2.1_4: ca gantho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:3.1: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana8.29:4.1: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava. (Sabbattha vitthāro.)
